* {{Cite book |author={{ill|Kaifu Yawotome|ja|海部やをとめ|12=draft}} & {{ill|Mitsuhashi Ken|ja|三橋健|12=draft}} |title=Yamatohime-no-Mikoto-sama no Monogatari |publisher=Fuyōsha International |date=2018}}

