1=Mikannagi Kiyonao|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q6537624}} have revealed that the text was based on ''{{ill|Daijingū Honki|ja|太神宮本紀|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Daijingū Honki|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}},'' an ancient document of [[:en:Ise Shrine|Ise Shrine]], and incorporated traditional legends of the shrine.<ref name="Osumi1977p368"/>

